race.description: Cup Hospitality Packages On Sale Now Maiden Plate
race.comment: BRAVO SIX (5) eye-catching debut at the big odds when eighth over 1400m at Wagga. Expected to have come on since and will keep improving as he gets out in trip. HELLS SPIRIT (6) looking for the mile deep into the prep and ticks plenty of boxes today. Strong through the line when second over 1400m at Corowa. Shapes as a genuine top-three player. HARRY CAVIAR (3) yet to draw a decent gate this time in and today is no different. Covered plenty of ground from the gate when up in class and trip with a poor ninth over 1600m at Seymour. Finds a weaker contest and not to be overlooked. DEFLECTOR (8) was below her best last time when midfield over 1400m at Wagga. Generally going well however, with placings at two of four starts this preparation. In the mix.
